         <abstract>
            <p>We prove that some extended Clenshaw-Curtis quadrature rules have all weights positive. We also present extended Filippi rules of open type having all weights positive. Conjectures on the possibility of other positive quadrature rules embedded in Clenshaw-Curtis or Filippi rule are suggested.</p>
          </abstract>
